## Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/rpa-challenge-automation-playwright.git
```

Navigate to project folder:

```bash
cd rpa-challenge-automation-playwright
```

### Create Virtual Environment

```bash
python -m venv venv
```

Activate virtual environment:

Windows:

```bash
venv\Scripts\activate
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Install Playwright browsers:

```bash
playwright install
```

## Running Tests

Run the automation:

```bash
pytest
```

Run with browser visible:

```bash
pytest --headed
```

Generate HTML Report:

```bash
pytest --html=reports/report.html --self-contained-html
```

## Automation Flow

1. Launch browser using Playwright
2. Navigate to RPA Challenge website
3. Click Start button
4. Read input data
5. Identify dynamic form fields
6. Fill all required fields
7. Submit records
8. Validate successful completion

